{#-
  v2.1.5 BL-333 / round-3 review fix C2: shared Jinja macro for brainstorm-content
  injection across PRD.md.j2 / APP_FLOW.md.j2 / BACKEND_STRUCTURE.md.j2.

  - Filename starts with `_` to signal a private partial (not iterated by
    `LpDefineRenderer.render_targets`; not part of `DOCS` in lp_define_runner.py).
  - Single source for the verify-and-edit marker comment that previously
    repeated 10x across the 3 docs.
  - Pipes content through `| markdown_safe` so a hostile
    `.launchpad/brainstorm-summary.md` cannot inject raw HTML / script tags.
    `_MARKDOWN_SAFE_CHARS` includes `<` and `>` so `<script>` renders as
    `\<script\>`.
-#}
{%- macro brainstorm_section(content) -%}
<!-- v2.1.5 BL-333: filled from .launchpad/brainstorm-summary.md — verify and edit. -->
{{ content | markdown_safe }}
{%- endmacro -%}
